headline: With 96% institutional ownership, Veralto Corporation (NYSE:VLTO) is a favorite amongst the big guns
summary: Given the large stake in the stock by institutions, Veralto's stock price might be vulnerable to their trading decisions The top 13 shareholders own 51% of the company Insiders have sold recently
